*1995. ''Philosophical Arguments''. [http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674664777 Harvard University Press]
*1999. ''A Catholic Modernity?''.
*2002. ''Varieties of Religion Today: William James Revisited''. [http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674012530 Harvard University Press]
*2004. ''Modern Social Imaginaries''. Duke University Press.
*2007. ''[[A Secular Age]]''. [http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674026766 Harvard University Press]
*2011. ''[http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674284364 Dilemmas and Connections: Selected Essays].''  Harvard University Press.
*2015. With Hubert Dreyfus, ''[http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674967519 Retrieving Realism].'' Harvard University Press.
*2016. ''[http://www.hup.harvard.edu/catalog.php?isbn=9780674660205 The Language Animal: The Full Shape of the Human Linguistic Capacity]'', Harvard University Press.

